title: NVIDIA Corp. stock rises Friday, outperforms market
text:
Shares of NVIDIA Corp. 
        NVDA,
        +3.12%
       rose 4.17% to $594.91 Friday, on what proved to be an all-around favorable trading session for the stock market, with the S&P 500 Index 
        SPX,
        -0.14%
       rising 1.23% to 4,839.81 and the Dow Jones Industrial Average 
        DJIA,
        -0.77%
       rising 1.05% to 37,863.80. This was the stock's second consecutive day of gains. NVIDIA Corp. hit a new 52-week high, surpassing its previous peak of $576.00, which the company reached on January 18th. Trading volume (53.7 M) eclipsed its 50-day average volume of 42.1 M.
